OL,3,CMum of murdered teen makes knife crime
OL,4,Cplea as three people jailed
OL,6,FThe mother of a murdered teenager has
OL,7,Fsaid the death of her son "should not
OL,8,Fjust be another statistic".
OL,10,FMohanad Goobe died after being stabbed
OL,11,Fduring an 'escalating conflict'
OL,12,Fbetween two rival groups in Moss Side,
OL,13,FManchester, on 15 September 2025.
OL,15,FA 16-year-old boy and a 15-year-old
OL,16,Fboy were convicted of murder, and a 14-
OL,17,Fyear-old boy was found guilty of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter, following a trial at
OL,19,FBolton Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
