PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779383153
OL,3,CMum of murdered teen makes knife crime
OL,4,Cplea as three people jailed
OL,6,FMohanad's mum Amaley made an
OL,7,Fimpassioned plea to anyone thinking of
OL,8,Fcarrying a knife, as her son's
OL,9,Fattackers were sentenced today, 21 May.
OL,11,FIn her victim impact statement read to
OL,12,Fcourt, she said: "I want people
OL,13,Fhearing this statement to understand
OL,14,Fthat Mohanad was taken from us without
OL,15,Fa thought for the consequences, and is
OL,16,Fdeath should never of happened.
OL,18,F"Knife crime, sadly, is becoming
OL,19,Fprevalent among our children, but the
OL,20,Fdeath of my son should not just be
OL,21,Fanother statistic.
OL,26,@tD@ROUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
