FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779383153
OL,3,CMum of murdered teen makes knife crime
OL,4,Cplea as three people jailed
OL,6,F"Mohanad was a living breathing,
OL,7,Flarger-than-life, lovable, sometimes
OL,8,Fcheeky, 15-year-old boy, whose life
OL,9,Fended when another child made a
OL,10,Fchoice, to take a knife out with them,
OL,11,Fand chose to use that knife on my son.
OL,13,F"A choice that killed my son, and
OL,14,Fended our lives as we knew it. I feel
OL,15,Fmany emotions, including anger, for
OL,16,Fthe boys responsible for my son's
OL,17,Fdeath, but I also feel pity, for they
OL,18,Ftoo will have to live with the
OL,19,Fconsequences of what they have done
OL,20,Fand I hope they see Mohanad's face for
OL,21,Fthe rest of their lives.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
