OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779383153
OL,3,CMum of murdered teen makes knife crime
OL,4,Cplea as three people jailed
OL,6,F"He wasn't in a gang, and he had never
OL,7,Fbeen in trouble with the police.
OL,9,F"A fallout between a group of boys
OL,10,Fresulted in Mohanad losing his life.
OL,11,FWhy has it become the norm for our
OL,12,Fyouths of today to think it is cool to
OL,13,Fcarry knives?"
OL,15,FThe convicted teenagers, who can't be
OL,16,Fnamed for legal reasons, were
OL,17,Fsentenced today at Bolton Crown Court.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@NO]
