OL,3,CMum of murdered teen makes knife crime
OL,4,Cplea as three people jailed
OL,6,FBoy A and Boy B were both handed the
OL,7,Fyouth equivalent of a life sentence,
OL,8,Fand ordered to serve 19 years and 18
OL,9,Fyears respectively. Boy C was handed a
OL,10,Fdeterminate six year sentence. The
OL,11,Fdefendants cannot be named for legal
OL,12,Freasons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
